---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Arkloop Developers" description="Arkloop 开发者门户，包含工程文档、API 参考与研究文章。" locale="zh" pathname="/" alternatePath="/en">
  <div class="home-shell">
    <section class="home-landing">
      <h1 class="home-title">Arkloop 开发者站</h1>
      <p class="home-tagline">开源 AI Agent 平台，集自主执行、智能搜索与沙箱运行时于一体。</p>
      <div class="home-actions">
        <a class="primary-button" href="/docs/guide">快速开始</a>
        <a class="secondary-button" href="/api">查看 API</a>
      </div>
      <nav class="home-aux-links">
        <a href="/research">Research</a>
        <span class="home-aux-sep">/</span>
        <a href="/docs/guide">Docs</a>
      </nav>
    </section>

    <section class="home-features">
      <div class="home-feature">
        <h3 class="home-feature-title">Agent Loop</h3>
        <p class="home-feature-desc">多步自主执行，支持规划、推理与工具编排。跨会话持久化记忆。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="home-feature">
        <h3 class="home-feature-title">Multi-Model</h3>
        <p class="home-feature-desc">集成 OpenAI、Anthropic 及任何兼容接口。基于优先级的路由，自动处理限流。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="home-feature">
        <h3 class="home-feature-title">沙箱执行</h3>
        <p class="home-feature-desc">Firecracker 微虚拟机或 Docker 隔离环境。Python、数据分析、图表生成，严格资源限制。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="home-feature">
        <h3 class="home-feature-title">浏览器自动化</h3>
        <p class="home-feature-desc">无头浏览器作为原生 Agent 工具。基于 Playwright 的网页交互、数据提取与截图。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="home-feature">
        <h3 class="home-feature-title">自定义 Personas</h3>
        <p class="home-feature-desc">专用 Agent 配置：独立提示词、工具集与行为层级。支持 Lua 自定义执行器。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="home-feature">
        <h3 class="home-feature-title">REST + SSE API</h3>
        <p class="home-feature-desc">40+ 端点覆盖线程、运行、Personas 与模型供应商。单调事件序、游标续传。</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
